{"tid":1451624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(必推) 小心匪諜 就在你身邊——提防隱藏式耳機","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T20:10:18.000Z","uid":146717,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c18cc7fa9b08d04f113e1983e5bd10ab525fd88a","tid":1451624,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:43:45.000Z","msg":"當大家仲討論緊內鬼戴單耳定雙耳耳機、有線定無線耳機時，小心佢哋已經換咗一批隱藏式耳機，基本上你唔哄到勁近<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係完全睇唔出：</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFNSFjz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFNSFjz.png&h=f9b2f194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BS7Z4MG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBS7Z4MG.jpg&h=d6148bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有手足講過，會有女間諜！男手足可能見到對方係女性戒心會降低，或者唔方便檢查/留意。<br />\n<br />\n提防男手足有可能畀女間諜離間，出現真手足畀人屌返轉頭嘅局面！所以大家一定要小心，打醒十二分精神，唔好因為對方係靚仔/靚女就掉以輕心！<br />\n<br />\n保密防諜，人人有責！"},{"pid":"b804f02214a408655a2a0c045f65e0bdc144c524","tid":1451624,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:45:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"76d730eb3ac25ababea802bba1e2a20e08505180","tid":1451624,"uid":192587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:46:11.000Z","msg":"推 大家醒水"},{"pid":"d6fa335fce5942aea668a7ad4b0bf5f4141b9049","tid":1451624,"uid":103476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:46:33.000Z","msg":"係時候學識反擊打狗啦！非常重要，借位一用<br />\n<br />\n致所有比狗打而想反抗嘅前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448193</a>"},{"pid":"1f7bca5cd81f1c4d0dcef87e7bc8332d172c4b1d","tid":1451624,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:46:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以眼還眼 黑警死全家！<br />\n心態改變命運<br />\n人數決定一切<br />\n<br />\n你 班 仆 街 幾 時 先 肯 無 限 期 四 罷？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://